<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="{{or page.attributes.lang 'en'}}">
  <head>
{{> head}}
  </head>
  <body class="home">
{{> header}}
    <main class="home-main">

      <section class="hero">
        <p class="page-ref">ref crcf</p>
        <p class="hero-eyebrow">Single-user · self-hosted · CNCF-conformant Kubernetes</p>
        <h1 class="hero-title">Your own platform for the<br><span class="accent">entire AI/ML lifecycle</span></h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">Get a model, fine-tune it, build apps that consume it, and serve it — on
          your own hardware, with the power of Kubernetes and none of the Kubernetes knowledge required.</p>
        <div class="hero-cta">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="../install/overview.html">Get started</a>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="start-here/what-is-thinkube.html">What is Thinkube?</a>
        </div>

        <ol class="loop" aria-label="The Thinkube AI/ML loop">
          <li class="loop-node"><span class="loop-num">1</span><span class="loop-label">Get models</span></li>
          <li class="loop-node"><span class="loop-num">2</span><span class="loop-label">Fine-tune</span></li>
          <li class="loop-node"><span class="loop-num">3</span><span class="loop-label">Build apps</span></li>
          <li class="loop-node"><span class="loop-num">4</span><span class="loop-label">Serve</span></li>
        </ol>
      </section>

      <section class="cockpit">
        <div class="cockpit-copy">
          <span class="kicker">The cockpit</span>
          <h2 class="section-h">You operate it by talking to Claude</h2>
          <p class="cockpit-lead">No dashboard to learn. You work in code-server, and Thinkube's whole
            control plane is exposed to Claude as <strong>MCP tools</strong> — deploys, models, GPUs,
            services. One conversation drives the platform; the GitOps loop does the rest in about a
            minute and a half.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="codewin" role="img"
             aria-label="A Claude Code session: deploy a template and load a model, driven by MCP tools.">
          <div class="codewin-bar">
            <span class="codewin-dots"><i></i><i></i><i></i></span>
            <span class="codewin-title">code-server — claude</span>
          </div>
<pre class="codewin-body" aria-hidden="true"><code><span class="c-prompt">›</span> <span class="c-user">deploy the vLLM template and load Llama-3.1-8B</span>

<span class="c-claude">●</span> Deploying the template and loading the model.
  <span class="c-ok">✓</span> <span class="c-tool">deploy_template</span><span class="c-paren">(</span>tkt-vllm-gradio<span class="c-paren">)</span>       <span class="c-dim">→ Gitea › Argo › Kaniko › Harbor › ArgoCD</span>
  <span class="c-ok">✓</span> <span class="c-tool">load_llm_model</span><span class="c-paren">(</span>meta-llama/Llama-3.1-8B<span class="c-paren">)</span>  <span class="c-dim">→ served on GPU</span>

  Your app is live at <span class="c-link">vllm-gradio.thinkube.com</span> <span class="c-dim">— ready in ~90s.</span></code></pre>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="journeys">
        <h2 class="section-h">Where to next</h2>
        <div class="card-grid">
          <a class="card" href="../install/overview.html">
            <span class="card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="6" rx="1"/><rect x="3" y="14" width="18" height="6" rx="1"/><line x1="7" y1="7" x2="7" y2="7"/><line x1="7" y1="17" x2="7" y2="17"/></svg>
            </span>
            <span class="card-kicker">Set up</span>
            <h3 class="card-title">Get Thinkube running</h3>
            <p class="card-desc">Install on your own machines — discovery, SSH, GPUs, networking — then put the installer away for good.</p>
            <span class="card-arrow">Set up <em>→</em></span>
          </a>
          <a class="card" href="how-you-work/index.html">
            <span class="card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="16" rx="1.5"/><polyline points="7 9 10 12 7 15"/><line x1="13" y1="15" x2="17" y2="15"/></svg>
            </span>
            <span class="card-kicker">How you work</span>
            <h3 class="card-title">code-server + Claude</h3>
            <p class="card-desc">Operate the whole platform by talking to Claude in your editor — MCP drives the rest.</p>
            <span class="card-arrow">Learn the cockpit <em>→</em></span>
          </a>
          <a class="card" href="lifecycle/index.html">
            <span class="card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-2.64-6.36"/><polyline points="21 3 21 8 16 8"/></svg>
            </span>
            <span class="card-kicker">The lifecycle</span>
            <h3 class="card-title">Run the loop</h3>
            <p class="card-desc">Models, fine-tuning, building apps, serving them — the full AI/ML lifecycle, step by step.</p>
            <span class="card-arrow">Start the loop <em>→</em></span>
          </a>
          <a class="card" href="reference/thinkube-yaml.html">
            <span class="card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 5.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 5.5 4H20v14H5.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 4 19.5z"/><line x1="8" y1="8" x2="16" y2="8"/><line x1="8" y1="11.5" x2="13" y2="11.5"/></svg>
            </span>
            <span class="card-kicker">Reference</span>
            <h3 class="card-title">Look it up</h3>
            <p class="card-desc">thinkube.yaml, the control panel, templates, components — precise and complete.</p>
            <span class="card-arrow">Browse reference <em>→</em></span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

    </main>
{{> footer}}
  </body>
</html>
